og|CONSTRAINT_CATALOG|  \n|m_szConstraintSchema|CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA|  \n|m_szConstraintName|CONSTRAINT_NAME|  \n  \n## Requirements  \n **Header:** atldbsch.h  \n  \n## See Also  \n [CRestrictions Class](../../data/oledb/crestrictions-class.md)"}